<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢١٢٢ <span class="c2">(م)</span> - قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">سُفْيَانُ </a>: قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4153">عُبَيْدُ اللهِ </a>: أَخْبَرَنِي: <span class="c2">«أَنَّهُ رَأَى نَافِعَ بْنَ جُبَيْرٍ أَوْتَرَ بِرَكْعَةٍ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>